(does that mean magicians and wizards shouldn't be able to do it in game?  I don't think so.)<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Again it comes down to the difference between a <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>nerf</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> and <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>re-balancing</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> a class.<br>
<br>
For a start VI chose the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>worst</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> way to nerf monk mitigation.  Removing AAXP mitigation abilities (from monks) and adding AAXP damage increasing abilities would have been much more sensible (although much more work for VI).  Therefore hitting monk mitigation were it starts to occasionally become an issue.<br>
<br>
Rather than nerfing monk base mitigation from L 1 (being the easiest if most messy option) and then allow monk to 'buy' some mitigation back post L55.<br>
<br>
<br>
IF they <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>must</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> leave in a base mitigation nerf, then they need to add a small base (probably damage table) damage increase, to allow monks to have a role again. (that of damage dealer that can't take a hit - currently they've got the can't take a hit, but the damage is sub par compared to other classes).<br>
<br>
Even FD pulling has been affected by the nerf, compounded by the fact that most monk avoidance skills only work from the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>FRONT</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.<br>
<br>
<br>
VI needs to realise Rogue-lite is <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">NOT</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> a valid role for a class. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=arothtb>Aroth TB</A> at: 12/4/02 9:13:34 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wezloc@themagicianstower>WEZLOC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 1342<br> <font color=#333333>(12/4/02 9:37:09 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_lightbulb.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: :(</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>You are just dumb, of course the pet is going to win with a DS up.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
